metadata.description:
Big Ben
a SOUVENIR from London, England!
Own your customized souvenir from the parallel world of Metaverse!
Meta Souvenirs are MICRO voxel worlds, inspired by the real and famous locations and monuments from around the UNIVERSE!
 each souvenir is a 1/1 NFT collection, which is animated by their identifying and cultural elements.
